*FvwmPagerFore #ffffff
*FvwmPagerBack #555555
*FvwmPagerHighlight #666666
*FvwmPagerFont -adobe-helvetica-bold-r-*-*-10-*-*-*-*-*-*-*
*FvwmPagerDeskTopScale 20
*FvwmPagerSmallFont 5x8
*FvwmPagerColumns 1
*FvwmPagerBalloons Pager
*FvwmPagerBalloonfore white



