The ButtonStyle command affects only the looks of the buttons.
Put this in your config file:

  Mouse 1 2 A Maximize 100 100
  Mouse 1 4 A Maximize 0 100
  Mouse 1 6 A Maximize 100 0
  Mouse 1 8 A Iconify

